Package edu.gatech.gtri.obm.alloy.translator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Alloy
    A class loads supporting libraries (Translator.als and utilities/*.als) and stores all signatures, fields, and facts data to be translated to an alloy file.
    AlloyExprFactory
    A utility class to create Alloy expression
    AlloyUtils
    A utility class related Alloy objects
    ClassesHandler
    Create signature and fields by tracing from main class to its properties to their property type classes and so on.
    ConnectorHandler
    A class to handle a connector
    ConnectorHandler_Transfer
    A handler for a transfer connector
    ConnectorsHandler
    Connectors handler
    ConnectorsHandler_OneOf
    A class to handle "Oneof" connector
    ExprVisitor
    Visitor to transform the Alloy object(signatures and facts) to a file.
    OBMXMI2Alloy
    A class to translate SysML Behavior Model in a xmi file into an alloy file.
    ToAlloy
    A helper class to translate OBMXMI to Alloy.
    UML2Utils
    Utility class for UML2 to extract informations
